{"tid":1637596,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"<突法>下周三(16號)，立法會重開","createTime":"2019-10-08T04:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T16:08:22.000Z","uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a33a68f79c3d1b540d57806113417fbff8b77021","tid":1637596,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"屌，立法會又開返<br />\n<br />\n立法會大會將於（16日）復會，特首林鄭月娥將會到立法會宣讀任內第三份《施政報告》。立法會主席梁君彥今天(8日)在會議廳外見記者，他表示為確保立法會順利復會，行管會決定於周三、周四發出黃色警示。<br />\n<br />\n至於林鄭會否其他方式宣讀《施政報告》，包括電視直播等，梁君彥表示沒有後備方案，又指按《議事規則》，並無規定特首每年都要到立法會宣讀《施政報告》，又強調最重要是確保立法會議員能夠順利和安全返回立法會。<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/383283/%E6%96%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E5%BE%A9%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%A4%BA-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5-%E7%84%A1%E5%BE%8C%E5%82%99%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F383283%2F%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%2589%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25A4%25BA-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2582%2599%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIvrdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=0d8acb37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/383283/%E6%96%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E5%BE%A9%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%A4%BA-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5-%E7%84%A1%E5%BE%8C%E5%82%99%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88</a>"},{"pid":"026da7deb926be8ac86bd8e9d40c35af9108c56e","tid":1637596,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e62c6fbb886509c5e0e140d4f005d52a44d6051c","tid":1637596,"uid":323301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"要全面裝修wo"},{"pid":"f6a64deb91eab023add79d21e7454fe7da0245e3","tid":1637596,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:55:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdee72cce3565d4b0d13dbc1a304c61463fbd4f7","tid":1637596,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:49:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c0fe5a1ed2c467d5b451e98fb3f22389ba585a9","tid":1637596,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:18:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"295dc033e2d90a2fd427789bbe83e057aa79c6bb","tid":1637596,"uid":299011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"支持泛民提彈劾林奠<br />\n<br />\n如立法會全體議員的四分之一聯合動議，指控行政長官有嚴重違法或瀆職行為而不辭職，經立法會通過進行調查，立法會可委托終審法院首席法官負責組成獨立的調查委員會，並擔任主席。調查委員會負責進行調查，並向立法會提出報告。如該調查委員會認為有足夠證據構成上述指控，立法會以全體議員三分之二多數通過，可提出彈劾案，報請中央人民政府決定"},{"pid":"e04fc45616ad131a359fd31890b3e9147edb919c","tid":1637596,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a72551a5b535a6d13516e97f7307f9b5caabd13","tid":1637596,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:05:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8379330efc9471e3c8581fde47858f89bf034c6a","tid":1637596,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:19:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a2b375c1da9323297dfa87d4c3665d2e0fc786c","tid":1637596,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"聽日立法會開返，大家真係唔關心下?"},{"pid":"ceda0bf10633c0ac157293aa871dd88117c024a3","tid":1637596,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"推"}]}